    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲爱的不可或缺的志愿者，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们想提前感谢您对这个畸变循环的测试。 您的参与对于我们进一步了解研究这项开创性科技来说不可或缺。 您付出的时间和努力，将会给我们提供无价的情报，从而推动科学进步和创新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们十分感激您的支持与信任。 您的贡献是迈向更光明、更先进未来的重要一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感激不尽的，<br>超好实验室</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157670/extras/8581f97807907c53abc667d7db797393.poster.avif?t=1762742542\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157670/extras/8581f97807907c53abc667d7db797393.webm?t=1762742542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157670/extras/8581f97807907c53abc667d7db797393.mp4?t=1762742542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畸变办公室的通关时间平均在30到120分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157670/extras/31c92191a131045eec3739d52d482c8c.poster.avif?t=1762742542\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157670/extras/31c92191a131045eec3739d52d482c8c.webm?t=1762742542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157670/extras/31c92191a131045eec3739d52d482c8c.mp4?t=1762742542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >包含内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过50处畸变</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在更高难度中探索，解锁额外区域。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全语音出演</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多结局</p></li><li><p class=